```
[0.0, 1.5, &#39;Hello&#39;, [&#39;Stack&#39;, 5.0], {&#39;a&#39;: {&#39;b&#39;: &#39;c&#39;}}]
```

- **dict**:

```python
class Backend(QtCore.QObject):
    @QtCore.pyqtSlot(result=&quot;QJsonObject&quot;)
    def return_dict(self):
        return {&quot;a&quot;: 1.5, &quot;b&quot;: {&quot;c&quot;: 2}, &quot;d&quot;: [1, &quot;3&quot;, &quot;4&quot;]}

    @QtCore.pyqtSlot(&quot;QJsonObject&quot;)
    def print_dict(self, ref):
        print(ref)
```

